    {
      "content": "This article covers the key things to keep in mind when planning to back up virtual machines in Azure.",
      "pos": [
        608,
        710
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If you've <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>prepared your environment<ept id=\"p1\">](backup-azure-vms-prepare.md)</ept>, this is the next step before you begin <bpt id=\"p2\">[</bpt>to backup VMs<ept id=\"p2\">](backup-azure-vms.md)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
        711,
        855
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "If you need more information about Azure virtual machines, see the <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>Virtual Machines documentation<ept id=\"p1\">](https://azure.microsoft.com/documentation/services/virtual-machines/)</ept>.",
      "pos": [
