      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "Azure Backup does not encrypt data as a part of the backup process.",
      "pos": [
        9808,
        9875
      ]
    },
    {
      "content": "However, you can encrypt data within the VM and back up the protected data seamlessly (read more about <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>backup of encrypted data<ept id=\"p1\">](backup-azure-vms-encryption.md)</ept>).",
      "pos": [
